Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天旋地转啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞接近 黑洞接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Game over Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 敏特机长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实体化全息投影？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就真的像在宇宙中飞行一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.40,title_op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(942,658.5)}ROLL RULER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是初级赛道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有中级和高级赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还想提升难度的话 你可以用琳达作为终端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去体验Extra赛道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个太空弹珠台感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于窜改琳达数据的犯人 他好像有点眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人叫卡露蒂娅·戈尔施密特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露蒂娅·戈尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈尔施密特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她名声不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个用强硬手段进行对局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而快速扩大势力的赌场老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她窜改了琳达的数据？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是卡露蒂娅命令她部下做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窜改数据的人 好像就是我们下一场对局的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场对局的对手指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露蒂娅看上的是我的霍华德度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她正式发来了挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要进行以霍华德度假村为赌注的Gate Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行Gate Battle？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 对莉欧的挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于Gate Holder来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着「不可拒绝Gate Battle」这样的默认规则在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可是例外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手可是窜改了琳达数据的卑鄙小人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行Gate Battle的话 世界上的赌场都会关注我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于空中度假村来说 可是有极大的宣传效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以霍华德度假村为赌注…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 你是不可能输的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德度假村的未来就寄托在你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么对局方式是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露蒂娅会再联系我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只知道对手的名字是 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.23,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}扑克牌中的J也是由Jack一词而来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁认识他么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在客人名单中没这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连是假名还是真名都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Gate Holder的话 有点相关传闻也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是琳达小姐曾经见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是窜改她数据的家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不记得犯人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来要是知道谁是对手的话 就能事先练习或制定对策了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 我们要去查明杰克的身份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要啊！等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好 回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到杰克脸的只有琳达啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？琳达你完全没有绘画细胞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10和9 庄家赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36连败 没有玩21点的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天灵灵地灵灵 佛祖保佑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花旗骰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被干掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩骰子也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连机器也抛弃他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 完全不是莉欧的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要接受挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂芙妮也说了 这次还是拒绝掉的好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我也习惯了老板的这种胡来行为了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧你人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我就是喜欢你这点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不接吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「又来」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直打来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分 到底是谁在恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是米萨莉城堡内的幽灵肖像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这东西会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这陪我 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是卡露蒂娅搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让莉欧你心理动摇 不能集中精力进行对局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默电话肯定也是一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 有我陪着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那时刚好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧你 一直温暖着我那被孤独环绕的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就轮到我来保护莉欧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这不是要跟丢了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟踪那个男的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟小孩子没关系 是大人的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是个小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝牛奶喝牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝牛奶喝牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士…芝士…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸奶酸奶酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是牛奶！牛奶 牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是缺氧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:57.37,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}还是…还是要牛奶…我要钙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在四千米高空中激烈运动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超级大笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样莉欧肯定能轻松获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧可！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟小孩子没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我叫敏特 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…杰克？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要玩这个还太小了点吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去对面喝点什么吧 我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来进行Gate Battle的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate Battle？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克·麦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露蒂娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这次的Gate Battle 是太空弹珠台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空弹珠台？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 说是Gate Battle啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在规定时间内得分高的一方获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在难度上 要选择Extra赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说Extra赛道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事霍华德也已经同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么说 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受对局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉从客人所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为对手是小孩子就大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敏特看到的杰克的能力是真的话 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事情多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了巧可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地来说这个的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和莉欧比赛的时候 也会用那个能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法之类的太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麦迪力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都一样 都是犯规嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯规啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟踪的那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个叫卡洛斯·田中的原Dealer吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底弄错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我为了不暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那个机器人姐姐记住了另外一个人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一族代代都是负责处理炸弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以比较擅长摆弄机器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是讨厌做那个才离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果连找口饭吃都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奄奄一息的时候 卡露蒂娅收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露蒂娅只是在利用我的麦迪力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会有那种能力的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的族人都有的 毕竟我们处理的是炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 为了保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然地具备了远距离操作的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和卡露蒂娅约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赢了这场比赛 我就能获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全息投影展开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个劲头 莉欧前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让陨石避开了太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克的麦迪力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲨鱼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧前辈 是机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧她是想享受这场比赛而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则中也是允许攻击对手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来左舷引擎被击毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞接近 黑洞接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 你太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分胜负现在才开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低糖少吃嘌呤类 血糖值就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No！决斗怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}日语中血糖和决斗同音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 撞坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 4 Phase 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我挡住陨石的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个厉害的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的Roll Ruler使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然是知道后才聘用她的吧 霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会是晴天会是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.59,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}麦克风测试时候常用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向绫和蔬菜店道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}お綾や八百屋にお謝り，一句日语绕口令，没什么含义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我彻底输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的英雄是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是感谢的一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是小熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我亲你还早了10年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧 蜉蝣是不吃东西的昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们在减肥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它们没嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是为了它们幼虫时代做的事还债吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}蜉蝣幼虫生活于水中，成虫不进食，寿命仅一天，\N后面的下集标题antlion多指蜉蝣的幼虫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼虫？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 也交给莉欧吧～
